QuestData.Title: Your First Fugueal Protolock
QuestData.Description: In order to aid my research you will need to decode various Progenitor cyphers like the Fugueal Protolock. This is a most difficult cypher, I will show you what you need to do.
QuestData.RewardText:
Well done, Maw Walker. That was truly an impressive effort.
Remember, that if you do struggle with these protolocks, your companion can help you overcome them if they have enough energy.
Now take your expanded knowledge out into the field.
